    "The remaining videos, which are effectively duplicates for the same coronary segment, are removed.",
    "While most of https://doi.org/10.1038/s41746-024-01134-4",
    "these duplicates are initially filtered out by Algorithm 2, there are instances where Algorithm 5 might reassign videos to the same segment.",
